## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="64983-102"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> 이벤트 발생만 때는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> 제어 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A> 속성을 설정 또는 해당 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A> 속성은 `true`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event occurs only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A> property is set or its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A> property is `true`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="64983-103">처리 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> 이벤트 처리기에 지정한 도구 설명 텍스트가 표시 됩니다 때마다는 마우스 포인터가 셀과 컨트롤 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ShowCellToolTips%2A> 속성 값은 `true`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-103">When you handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event, the ToolTip text you specify in the handler is shown whenever the mouse pointer is over a cell and the control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.ShowCellToolTips%2A> property value is `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64983-104"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> 이벤트는 현재 상태 또는 셀의 값에 의해 결정 되는 도구 설명 표시 하려는 경우에 유용 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-104">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event is useful when you want to display ToolTips determined by the current state or value of a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="64983-105"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> 이벤트는 또한 될 때마다 발생의 값은 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 검색 하거나 프로그래밍 방식으로 또는 마우스 포인터가 셀 내부로 이동할 때.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event also occurs whenever the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is retrieved, either programmatically or when the mouse pointer enters a cell.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="64983-106">사용할 수는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A> 상태 또는 셀의 값을 확인 하 고이 정보를 사용 하 여 설정할 속성을는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A> 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-106">You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.ColumnIndex%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellEventArgs.RowIndex%2A> properties to determine the state or value of a cell, and use this information to set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCellToolTipTextNeededEventArgs.ToolTipText%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64983-107">이 속성은 셀의 값으로 초기화 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> 이벤트 값을 무시 하는 속성입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-107">This property is initialized with the value of the cell <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> property, which the event value overrides.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="64983-108">처리는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> 많은 양의 데이터로 작업할 때 이벤트 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> 여러 셀에 대 한 값입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-108">Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellToolTipTextNeeded> event when working with large amounts of data to avoid the performance penalties of setting the cell <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.ToolTipText%2A> value for multiple cells.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="64983-109">자세한 내용은 참조 [Windows Forms DataGridView 컨트롤의 크기 조정에 대 한 유용한](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/best-practices-for-scaling-the-windows-forms-datagridview-control.md)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="64983-109">For more information, see [Best Practices for Scaling the Windows Forms DataGridView Control](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/best-practices-for-scaling-the-windows-forms-datagridview-control.md).</span></span>  
  
